reviews.text: This is a great restaurant which was recommended to me by work colleagues and happened to pass by it a few days later. I have visited a few times since and the food has been very good on each occasion. The restaurant itself is not fancy but all you need for a good meal, be ready to share a table with strangers. The prices are very good and cheap for Hong Kong. This will be a weekly visit for me.
Fun place especially if you get to know the staff. Simple ok food and is pretty cheap. Open 24 hrs so that's a bonus.

Great place for a quick meal in the heart of Wan Chai. Has variety of roasted meats in the traditional Chinese style.
Walk in service, no need to book
Great place for tasty Hong Kong BBQ, saltes meats and rice dishes. Fast and open 22 hrs just perfect have a late night. Don't expect the best in town but enjoyed my visits here.

Bad, dishonest and distasteful. Ordered a mabo-bean curb and mushroom rice set. The menu clearly states that there is such set lunch that includes rice and soup but the worker argued otherwise. Trying to be nice and give it a chance due to the fact that we re in a rush. Nonetheless, food came out to unexpectedly bad and awful. Overcharged by 65HKD. 

AVOID AT ALL COSTS

Too bad.. The Roast Pork 脆皮烧肉 was not crunchy at all and the BBQ pork 蜜汁叉烧 was dry and not sweet at all. Overall not great

reviews.text: It was nice because roast duck is nice. But it was a pretty average version of it. Sauce was too salty and meat was slightly dry. And we asked the price of half duck before sitting down and then they tried to charge us double for eating in so we had to get it to take away and sit outside in the heat (159 instead of 80!)
超值美味的飯盒！餸菜有「麻婆豆腐」及「蘿蔔豆卜炆火腩」，加杯熱檸茶，合共四十六元。
鴨脾四寶飯 $68 跟餐有飲品，味道尚可，價錢略貴，好多遊客，坐得不太舒服。
主廚師傅忙到一個段落，就直接在廚房區域內抽菸、丟菸蒂。因為是緊鄰人行道邊的開放式廚房作業區，只是用透明玻璃隔開，看得一清二楚。
燒味好食，但鼓油咸了點，建議走色，有需要再自己落。
